{
  "stem": "24814.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went riding out with the tanks while we shot up some Germans who were trying to lay mine fields on the other side against our crossing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We crossed over, and we did some heavy fighting for two days south of the Danube, and then broke out toward the Alps.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And suddenly, we came over a hill, and I could see German prisoners as far as you could see them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thousands and thousands and thousands, the whole German army marching in demoralized-- beaten, weaponless, hands up, marching by-- I couldn't believe how many Germans I saw marching to the rear.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we pushed south toward the Danube-- beyond the Danube to the Alps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And our last goal was the next valley over from Oberammergau, the famous place where the Passion Play is put on every year.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there we were in the middle of the towering snow peaks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was our last position.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were ordered to hold in place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One of our combat commands of our division went racing on, and they liberated a fort where they were holding many distinguished prisoners, the premier of France and many other people, whom they had not quite killed yet.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they got into the castle, and the SS troops who were behind them attacked them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the odd thing was a German officer fought the SS troops to help them try and save the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were some decent Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was killed in the fighting, but they-- then our column came up, drove the SS off, and they saved the-- the premier of France, Daladier, and a bunch of other distinguished people.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
